  "id": "api/common/NgSwitch",
  "title": "NgSwitch",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/directives/ng_switch.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L35-L126\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0/packages/common/src/directives/ng_switch.ts#L35-L126\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/NgSwitch\", \"name\": \"NgSwitch\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"ngswitch\">NgSwitch<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#ngswitch\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">stable</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Adds / removes DOM sub-trees when the nest match expressions matches the switch expression.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"directive-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({ selector: '[<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]' })\nclass <a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#ngSwitch\">set ngSwitch: any</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"selectors\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">Selectors<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading selector\">\n  [<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]\n  </code-example>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"inputs\">\n  <h2 id=\"inputs\">Inputs<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#inputs\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <div class=\"input\">\n    <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a></code> bound to <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#ngSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch.ngSwitch</a></code>\n    \n  </div>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a></code> stamps out nested views when their match expression value matches the value of the\nswitch expression.</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">In other words:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>you define a container element (where you place the directive with a switch expression on the\n<code>[<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]=\"...\"</code> attribute)</li>\n<li>you define inner views inside the <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a></code> and place a <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code> attribute on the view\nroot elements.</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">Elements within <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a></code> but outside of a <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitchCase</a></code> or <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitchDefault</a></code> directives will\nbe preserved at the location.</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">The <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code> directive informs the parent <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a></code> of which view to display when the\nexpression is evaluated.\nWhen no matching expression is found on a <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code> view, the <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a></code> view is\nstamped out.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <h2 id=\"properties\">Properties<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table properties-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td><a id=\"ngSwitch\"></a>ngSwitch</td>\n        <td><label class=\"property-type-label\"><code>any</code></label></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n          \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage Notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example>\n    &#x3C;container-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]=\"switch_expression\">\n      &#x3C;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_1\">...&#x3C;/some-element>\n      &#x3C;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_2\">...&#x3C;/some-element>\n      &#x3C;some-other-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_3\">...&#x3C;/some-other-element>\n      &#x3C;ng-container *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_3\">\n        &#x3C;!-- use <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> ng-container to <a href=\"api/animations/group\" class=\"code-anchor\">group</a> <a href=\"api/forms/SelectMultipleControlValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">multiple</a> root nodes -->\n        &#x3C;inner-element>&#x3C;/inner-element>\n        &#x3C;inner-other-element>&#x3C;/inner-other-element>\n      &#x3C;/ng-container>\n      &#x3C;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a>>...&#x3C;/some-element>\n    &#x3C;/container-element>\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/NgSwitchCase\n - api/common/NgSwitchDefault\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/dynamic-form\n - guide/structural-directives\n - guide/template-syntax\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/animations/group\n - api/common\n - api/common/NgSwitch#description\n - api/common/NgSwitch#inputs\n - api/common/NgSwitch#ngSwitch\n - api/common/NgSwitch#ngswitch\n - api/common/NgSwitch#properties\n - api/common/NgSwitch#selectors\n - api/common/NgSwitch#usage-notes\n - api/common/NgSwitchCase\n - api/common/NgSwitchDefault\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/forms/SelectMultipleControlValueAccessor\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/directives/ng_switch.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L35-L126\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0/packages/common/src/directives/ng_switch.ts#L35-L126\n-->"
